{"tid":1822562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國民黨黃昭順：如果韓國瑜選輸，我就去跳蓮池潭！","createTime":"2020-01-13T04:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T14:03:20.000Z","uid":52658,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2220f5fd29a2eee424e429c4fcc4b86fb5c24c08","tid":1822562,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"2020總統立委大選，高雄民進黨8席立委全部當選，「八仙過海」。當初國民黨立委候選人黃昭順，曾在鏡頭前對韓國瑜說「輸了要跳蓮池潭」，昨夜網友也紛紛呼籲黃昭順，「蓮池潭在等你了，快給我跳下去吧。」<br />\n<br />\n黃昭順日前與韓國瑜同框，她幽默地說，「我跟你講，選輸、輸了要跳蓮池潭。」一旁的韓國瑜則笑答「哈哈，你自己要跳喔。」這段對話的影片也被網友翻出來，甚至有網友在臉書發起「看黃昭順跳蓮池潭」的活動頁面，竟然引來1.2萬人響應、7.3萬人有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n還有網友跑到黃昭順的臉書留言，「什麼時候要跳蓮池潭？」、「要跟王世堅一樣說到做到」、「好期待」、「誠信問題很重要喔」、「可以不跳，但請直接退出政壇」、「不要說話不算話」等，黃昭順緊急關閉臉書粉專，目前無法搜尋。"},{"pid":"b599c94644941cc1f4665356b90edfffd991fdb9","tid":1822562,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ad536e625acedfe830cb9536cfc6842449d306a","tid":1822562,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d94fc9c49beaa596876b8ce5d4811610c651296","tid":1822562,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:18:42.000Z","msg":"佢已經縮咗沙<br />\n<br />\n【台灣大選】香港未來預想圓－－建立香港媒體、文化、Youtuber圈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1822576\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1822576</a>"},{"pid":"615fcf3bdc15473e5e46523679c8a9c2a40ac1a8","tid":1822562,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5128528a8dfa2859f13456c4707f389baf468fc","tid":1822562,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"057cae427b1f512994c0d2677454216357d28a32","tid":1822562,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:45:02.000Z","msg":"快啲找數"},{"pid":"d913bb6607ff29e0fe93517d26e519011e5028f8","tid":1822562,"uid":127447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"支那人從來冇口齒"}]}